  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0011",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021",
    "primary_id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_25",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 8,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_25",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Brody recalls 'painful' experience of making 'The Pianist'",
        "bbox": [
          0.2824242424242424,
          0.5850980392156863,
          0.4890909090909091,
          0.600156862745098
        ],
        "order": 22
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_30",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "America. Even in spite of assimilating and becoming Americans, you're still a foreigner.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.7375757575757576,
          0.5854117647058823,
          0.9551515151515152,
          0.6067450980392157
        ],
        "order": 24
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_22",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Aries (March 21-April 19). Juggling business expectations? Mercury's entrance to Capricorn helps to keep all your professional pins in the air!",
        "bbox": [
          0.04424242424242424,
          0.5888627450980393,
          0.25393939393939396,
          0.6174117647058823
        ],
        "order": 25
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_26",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"Brutalist\" spans several decades, beginning as László lands in Pennsyl- vania after World War II, where he shovels coal and bunks in his cousin's storage closet. Once a celebrated ar- chitect in his native Hungary, he even- tually is scooped up by a wealthy in- dustrialist (Guy Pearce), who commis- sions László to design and build an ex- orbitant community center. But even as he and his wife Erzsébet (Felicity Jones) attempt to forge a new life, they are constantly exploited and reminded they are \"other.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.283030303030303,
          0.6067450980392157,
          0.49272727272727274,
          0.6779607843137255
        ],
        "order": 26
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_31",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "For Corbet, casting Brody was \"very clear because of his family history,\" the director says. What's more, \"he just felt so incredibly emotionally available; so graceful and so pained. I mean, he really just wore his heart on his sleeve.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.7369696969696969,
          0.6073725490196078,
          0.953939393939394,
          0.6494117647058824
        ],
        "order": 27
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_28",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Brody was struck by the \"complexity\" and \"nuance\"of Corbet's script, which he co-wrote with his partner, filmmaker Mona Fastvold.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5060606060606061,
          0.6139607843137255,
          0.7242424242424242,
          0.6425098039215686
        ],
        "order": 28
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Taurus (April 20-May 20). Leaning into your logical side? As Mercury enters Capricorn, adopting a pragmatic tone helps you communicate your point.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04424242424242424,
          0.6211764705882353,
          0.25272727272727274,
          0.6497254901960784
        ],
        "order": 29
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_29",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"It's unfortunately taken me decades to find something like this,\" Brody says. \"It's such an ambitious thing. But also, it instantly tapped into my mother and grandparents' struggle of coming to",
        "bbox": [
          0.5066666666666667,
          0.6431372549019608,
          0.7242424242424242,
          0.6782745098039216
        ],
        "order": 30
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0012",
    "kind": "text_cluster_panel",
    "page": "newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021",
    "primary_id": "mineru_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_021_32",
